  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tFresh<br />\n\tFresh is something newly made or prepared. What is the fresh item? Where is it available? How is it obtained?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They took a breath of fresh air... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) walk into a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bakery\" target=\"_blank\">bakery</a> and smell freshly baked bread<br />\n\t2) garden salad made with fresh vegetables<br />\n\t3) fresh water is a precious resource<br />\n\t4) a fresh haircut<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAs the warm water continued to run through his hair and down his back, he gently touched the scar on his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/forearm\" target=\"_blank\">forearm</a>. It did not hurt anymore, but it did remind him of unfinished business. After getting out of the shower, he went back to his room. In fresh, clean clothes, Wolfe was sitting on his bed drying his hair as he <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/flip\" target=\"_blank\">flip</a>ped through a magazine. A fashion magazine was not usually on his reading list. This edition of the magazine, however, was a special gift from the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/intern\" target=\"_blank\">intern</a> at work.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161967241161/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721258/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721258\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724407/\">如何精通多国语言 李光耀的5大学习心得</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724374/\">新加坡国父李光耀去世 享年91岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723278/\">毁男神：高富帅达西先生靠贩卖奴隶赚钱？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724410/\">世界水日：9个时刻最该喝水</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724378/\">平均身高1米7 现代明星都是小矮人?!</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626558/\">比简单重复更有效的记忆方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p630412/\">25个最常弄错含义的单词（1）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p703957/\">机票何时买最便宜 起飞8周前的周日</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724208/\">一饱眼福！这10个国家总是产美女！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724413/\">囧研究: 一日三餐真的好吗？ </a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a 