  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201304/b96c15e8-d587-4750-be0c-ade426490feb.jpg\" style=\"height: 371px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722338\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBut in recent years, the world's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/offshore\" target=\"_blank\">offshore</a> havens have found themselves under unprecedented pressure to open up their books to lift the veil of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/secrecy\" target=\"_blank\">secrecy</a> that protects their clients. This call for reform has been led, says Gabriel Zucman, a tax expert based at the Paris School of Economics, by the United States.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;People use the fact that in offshore tax havens, you have bank secrecy, so <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/basically\" target=\"_blank\">basically</a> you can have a bank account in Switzerland. And if you do not declare it on your tax return, then you can evade taxes on your <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/income\" target=\"_blank\">income</a>, interest and dividends that you earn on this Swiss bank account.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;So <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/essentially\" target=\"_blank\">essentially</a>, I just shovel my money into a bank account in Switzerland, don't tell anyone about it. The Swiss authorities or the Luxembourg authorities, or whoever they are, don't tell my, read my, the authorities in the country which I'm based, and therefore no one knows about this money. It's that simple?&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;Absolutely. That's bank secrecy. There is no automatic exchange of bank information between the banks in tax havens and foreign tax authorities. And that's the main problem, and that's what makes tax <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/evasion\" target=\"_blank\">evasion</a> possible.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: verdana, arial; border-bottom: rgb(0,90,148) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,90,148); line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722338/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722338\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724407/\">如何精通多国语言 李光耀的5大学习心得</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724374/\">新加坡国父李光耀去世 享年91岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723278/\">毁男神：高富帅达西先生靠贩卖奴隶赚钱？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724410/\">世界水日：9个时刻最该喝水</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724378/\">平均身高1米7 现代明星都是小矮人?!</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626558/\">比简单重复更有效的记忆方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p630412/\">25个最常弄错含义的单词（1）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p703957/\">机票何时买最便宜 起飞8周前的周日</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724208/\">一饱眼福！这10个国家总是产美女！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724413/\">囧研究: 一日三餐真的好吗？ </a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
